item.title: FexCubes
item.description: This project was made to show how I started my career as a web developer and web designer, as well as to prove to myself that you do not need to be afraid to expose your code for viewing. You can't please everyone.

item.title: FrogsTicket
item.description: This is a Discord bot for ticket system. Allows you to create a discord, a ticket system on your server, namely, an appeal to the administration or the task of important questions in a separate chat with the administration

item.title: FrogsTeam (FT)
item.description: FrogsTeam (FT) - This community of developers and ordinary people was created in order to have fun killing time, as well as looking for friends and help for novice developers.

item.title: About
item.description: I am currently in Ukraine, and I work remotely on the FrogsTeam project, MCHoster. In my free time, I go in for sports, study something interesting and keep a blog, as well as working on projects on github or constantly trying myself in different fields of activity.
